author: chamikara
msg: Added basic features needed to support new OASIS WSRX committee specification as given below.
Made rm namespace a paramenter of the RM elements.
Moved the constants to two different interfaces (SPEC_2005_02 and SPEC_2005_10).
Made corrections to make server side support both namespaces. (namespace of a sequence is decided based on the namespace of the create sequence message).
Made corrections to make client side support both namespaces (namespace can be configured by setting a constant in the client API).
Basic scenarios are working for both namespaces.
